WEBVTT

00:06.441 --> 00:08.182
- Previously on
"Briarpatch"...

00:09.618 --> 00:12.012
- It appears that someone just
blew up the landlady.

00:12.055 --> 00:13.926
- No one lives
in that apartment.

00:13.970 --> 00:16.016
Certainly not my sister.

00:16.059 --> 00:17.974
- Okay, I can
show you something.

00:18.018 --> 00:19.889
Where Felicity actually lived.

00:19.932 --> 00:21.499
[car engine starts]

00:21.543 --> 00:23.588
- [gasps]
- Serial bomber is a new one.

00:23.632 --> 00:26.330
I wanted to let you know
we've identified our man.

00:26.374 --> 00:28.158
He's Ferness.
- You're the boyfriend.

00:28.202 --> 00:30.334
- I need you to know
I didn't do it.

00:30.378 --> 00:32.467
You watch, there'll be a full
manhunt by tomorrow lunch.

00:33.903 --> 00:35.122
- Damn it.

00:35.165 --> 00:36.123
[heavy breathing]

00:36.166 --> 00:38.038
- So who did it?

00:38.081 --> 00:40.127
- Lalo, get us some Cognac.

00:40.170 --> 00:42.085
- All right.
You want the good stuff?

00:42.129 --> 00:44.218
- Bring him the good stuff.
- You're funeral, Miss Dill.

00:44.261 --> 00:45.654
- They found Clyde Brattle,
Jake.

00:45.697 --> 00:47.351
- Part time
American gun runner,

00:47.395 --> 00:49.266
full time
international fugitive.

00:49.310 --> 00:50.528
- Safe to assume he's headed
this way.

00:50.572 --> 00:52.182
Senator only needs one of you.

00:52.226 --> 00:53.531
- What you been waiting for?

00:53.575 --> 00:55.098
- Immunity only comes
in exchange

00:55.142 --> 00:56.795
for an honest testimony.

00:56.839 --> 00:59.668
- Oh, you're little Senator's
gonna ride my testimony

00:59.711 --> 01:01.104
all the way
to the White House, baby.

01:01.148 --> 01:04.281
- [grunting]

